                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="apa-arti-dari-yaumul-taghabun-yaumul-tanad-yaumul-wakiahyaumul-khulud">
                            16. apa arti dari   yaumul taghabun ,yaumul tanad, yaumul wakiah,yaumul khulud</h2><br />
                        Yaumul taghabun = hari terbukanya segala goncangan<br />Yaumul tanah = hari panggilan<br />Yaumul wakiah = hati kejatuhan<br />Yaumul khulud = yang kekal<br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="hari-kebangkitan-disebut-dengan-a-yaumul-baasb-yaumul-mizanc-yaumul-hisabd-yaumul-yazatolong-cepat-ya-dijawab%e2%80%8b">
                            17. hari kebangkitan disebut dengan...A yaumul ba"asB yaumul mizanC yaumul hisabD yaumul yazatolong cepat ya dijawab​</h2><br />
